@startuml State Diagram - Emergency Access
title Emergency Access State Diagram

[*] --> Disabled
Disabled --> Enabled : Patient enables
Enabled --> Requested : Responder requests access
Requested --> Granted : System validates & logs
Granted --> Completed : Data accessed
Completed --> [*]

Requested --> Denied : Access denied
Denied --> [*]

Granted --> Revoked : Patient revokes
Revoked --> [*]
@enduml
